data.text:
Find out more about the galleries who will be joining us at CHART 2024. In this candid series of interviews, founders and directors of leading galleries from across the Nordics reveal how they got their start in the industry, whose work they collect and the all important answer as to where you should sit at a gallery dinner.

Keep up to date with the latest shows opening at leading galleries across the Nordic region. Featuring exhibition recommendations for each of the Nordic capitals, our Art Calendar is your one-stop-shop for everything related to contemporary art. Whether you are planning a weekend break, looking for new shows in your own city or just want to stay in-the-know, we've got you covered.
